<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201125/278ef30c5df54fcebc20491d6a3f2ddf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乔延年自跋《七律》古才女集锦图。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">卓文君：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它宵莫比此宵良，风动芭蕉月转廊。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">修妥三生缘共枕，听成一曲凤求凰。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">接书这日回诗柬，可记当年卖酒浆？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">愧使相如归故里，八揖感泪拜糟糠！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201125/57f7e75234964bb1b11cff9513cc2be4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乔延年自跋《七律》古才女集锦图。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">严蕊：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">踏野回思囹圄煎。朱熹愧否已失贤？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">投来凡世尤为苦，沦入风尘更觉难。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">妙语成词伏自悯，清明判释有他怜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">萍踪蓬影迷归处，女子姝才不是安！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201125/43170a6428874fa5add84bd6e4deeeae.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乔延年自跋《七律》古才女集锦图。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蔡文姬：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">十八拍诉舛沉陈，何必黄金赎此身？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">汉使催程哭上路，胡夫缱绻泪沾襟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">参商有意相逢欠，母子无辜两念深。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">阿满缘玄来作苦，最苦从昔是女人！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201125/dc08168a818f41e9bca57249d9f3879d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乔延年自跋《七律》古才女集锦图。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">班昭：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">抒情作画起思量，貌美才高命舛尝。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">赋就东征驱苦闷，日行西陆守孤霜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">月园尤比亏时少，路坦多移蹇径长。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">雷雨交加花未谢，翻读汉史有精章。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201126/5c06f45c9c0b44c5872f88f7533f1e74.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乔延年自跋《七律》古才女集锦图。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鱼玄机：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">落入玄门谁可怜？李郎心变牡丹残！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">八叉诗彩无俗和，三载婚悲是孽缘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">气斥贫婢失忍字，魂消酷法遇仇官。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才高貌美文垂史，叹也迟蒙武曌天。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201125/5a3c57da699d40c8ab685f9dfd55d22b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乔延年自跋《七律》古才女集锦图。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朱淑贞：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才嫒何故每嘘咳？是忖无辜降世来。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">配偶失闻求凰曲，接书未遇剪炷才。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">维生不欠柴兼米，动笔多为正转歪。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梁祝相怜飞牖过，观之欲感慕资哀！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201125/9fa172a69abd46a4b5878105b5345a00.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乔延年自跋《七律》古才女集锦图。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谢道韫：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">娴吟柳絮名垂史，持刃杀贼是虎贲。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爱子儒夫殂战火，孤孀寂舍着诗文。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">庭前闲草无屐迹，树上杂啼有鸟音。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">仰读佳作惟搜古，谢第王宅何处寻？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201125/08be31b8ab3244f9b527d5dd221f6210.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乔延年自跋《七律》古才女集锦图</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李冶：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">貌美才高果是悲，莫如村女总无为。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">芳龄五岁吟佳句，感叹双亲兆苦危。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">圣口出金笞杖落，娇躯化土魄魂飞。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">生辰未伴吉星辅，索命呈诗遇反贼！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201125/fbaec8758e404c079f921b2adbf03b39.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乔延年自跋《七律》古才女集锦图。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">薛涛。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">闲云野鹤自无羁，一代名媛一史奇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身若风摇萍藻影，愁如水涌浣花溪。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红笺诗苦真思隐，墨客言欢假话离。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">男子尤为功利重，谁怜泪点泫霞衣？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201125/e88bbf49dab345528b9cb57d4181dd02.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乔延年自跋《七律》古才女集锦图。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刘彩春：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">名媛才气满唐闻，不亚于时邓丽君。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">唱罢望夫愁敛靥，听得思女泪濡巾。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丹花比美羞失色，绿水和声愧哑琴。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大户千金无尽宠，小家碧玉也怜人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201125/b61350a740554c3aaafb8437616573ea.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乔延年自跋《七律》古才女集锦图。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">上官婉儿：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">书成圣旨细推敲，武后怜才花未凋。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">官觅宏程揖锦阙，诗求宠者斗风骚。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">龙池凤岭随时履，墨海文山任意翱。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">绝代佳人唐半主，宫庭政变惨失逃！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201125/95021ca9c4da48039c3e83e6f2a7cfab.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乔延年自跋《七律》古才女集锦图。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">花蕊夫人：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">回眸正起念乡心，秦岭巍巍隔蜀云。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">易主仍然怀旧主，承恩叵耐厌新恩。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如之孟昶怜文女，未必泉城怨美人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">十四万兵皆卸甲，娇娥何可善其身？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201125/f055e6db7dfe4ea0add72e267d388072.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乔延年自跋《七律》古才女集锦图。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">聂胜琼：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鹧鸪天词读感伤，思人不止断人肠。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">三更苦雨催凄泪，一盏孤灯对冷床。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">叶落风中嫌杜宇，莲开枕顶慕鸳鸯。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">怜惜正室牵红线，皓发双飘伴李郎。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201125/c8858f32c17449e6a97f476686c0ea51.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乔延年四体书法欣赏：篆书、隶书、正书、草书。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201125/9b90f3726c994ffd90f7a9168efa8430.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>